Subject: perf test: Read child test 10 times a second rather than 1
Git-commit: 5f2f051a9386aa6d62d081a9889ca321ca8c309b
Patch-mainline: v6.10-rc1
References: perf-sp7-v6.11-userspace-update

Make the perf test output smoother by timing out the poll of the child
process after 100ms rather than 1s.

